# üß† LangChain + Ollama + MySQL (MCP POC)

This is a Python proof-of-concept showing how to build an **AI Agent with LangChain**, powered by **Ollama** and a **MySQL database**, using **Model Context Protocol (MCP)**.

## ‚úÖ Features

- Query MySQL with natural language
- Powered by LangChain MCP and ChatOllama
- Auto-selects tools (SQL)
- Structured and extendable

